<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l20">herbſtmeſſe gen frankfurt / vnd vvıder darauſʒ / <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe cʒu ew 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan><ex>r</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l22">oder aber den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd des begern mit ſıcherm geleẏte <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_94_r2l21"><expan>günſtikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r2l24"> <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wollet 
<add><ab facs="#facs_94_r2l23"><expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> geleit vnd gepiete geet </ab></add> / Als etc / das wollen etc / <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc </ab>
