</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber etc. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>kauffl<ex>eute</ex></expan> etc.
                        in die <expan>nehstk<ex>ünfftige</ex></expan> herbstmesse gen Frankfurt und
                        wider darausz ,<expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie czu ew oder aber den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und des begern, mit sicherm geleyte
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<add><expan>günstikl<ex>ich</ex></expan></add>
<expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wollet,
                                <add><expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> geleit und gepiete geet</add>, als etc. Das
                        wollen etc. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztume<ex>n</ex></expan> von Asschaffemburgk.</ab>
</div>
